Type: Effect
Name: Heat
Initial DC: +2
Addt'l DC: +2
DC Bonus: +1 to Threat Die Size
Description: A [Effect]Heat Spell creates a intense, breif change in temperature. The effect causes a Threat[Heat], (Threat DC=10+1d6+Casting Stat). The effect of this spell can be intensified, increasing the Threat Dice Size. To increase the Threat Dice Size, add +2 to the Mana DC of the Spell Word, for every Threat Die step.
